See README in /home/Javier.Delgado/apps/nr_utils_dist/master/postproc/nems/tracker


The run_tracker.py and tracker_subsetter.py scripts are copied from there.


General intructions:
0. Prepare environment  - set paths in env.sh and source it
1. Set parameters in trk.conf
2. Run tracker_subsetter.py to generate the tracker input files from the UPP GriB files
3. Run prepare_tracker_dir.py to set links, modify namelist, etc.
4. Edit trk.nml
5. ./tracker.exe < trk.nml &> logfile

* To generate the three TC vitals plots - see nr_tracks.py. Note that this does not 
  use trk.conf, all parameters are set in the script.


